      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "A meeting Of the chamber will\nbe held at noon tomorrow and the\nreport of the two committees who\nwere appointed yesterday will be\nread. The committee who went to\ncall upon the 0. r. & N. will prob\nably have nothing to report as the\nlocal agent stated he would have\nto communicate with several men\nhigher up before he could say any,\nthing definite.\n\n\nThe Washington Water Power\ncompany committee will probably\nhave some report."
